## GOV.UK Prototype kit 

You'll need the prototype kit for creating interactive prototypes for user research (UR). We've pulled together some resources to help get you started with using the kit: 

 

Prototype kit – training before using the kit (DWP) 

https://dwp-design-manual.herokuapp.com/prototype-kit-training 

 

Prototype kit tutorials (GDS) 

https://govuk-prototype-kit.herokuapp.com/docs/tutorials-and-examples  

 

Tutorials and templates – GOV.UK Prototype Kit (govuk-prototype-kit.herokuapp.com) 

 

Prototype kit – downloading and installing  

https://govuk-prototype-kit.herokuapp.com/docs/install  

 

Prototype kit – getting started and branches (design community workshop with Rinto and Mike) 

https://educationgovuk-my.sharepoint.com/:v:/g/personal/mike_knight_education_gov_uk/EUZccw2HhlxDtfZs169esywB3esqzOh31S5JnhayVxnvwQ 

 

